HEADWORD: Inunctuosity
<hw>In*unc`tu*os"i*ty</hw> <pr>(?; 135)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The
lack of unctuosity; freedom from greasiness or oiliness; <as>as, the
<ex>inunctuosity</ex> of porcelain clay</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Kirwan.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
